p = Graph()
g = p | p
assert g.triples == []
assert g.top is None
assert g is not p
q = Graph([('a', ':instance', 'alpha')])
g = p | q
assert g.triples == [('a', ':instance', 'alpha')]
assert g.top == 'a'
assert g is not q is not p
r = Graph([('a', ':ARG', 'b'), ('b', ':instance', 'beta')], top='b')
g = q | r
assert g.triples == [('a', ':instance', 'alpha'), ('a', ':ARG', 'b'), ('b',
    ':instance', 'beta')]
assert g.top == 'a'
